Name: Vacation Adventures: Park Ranger 13
About the game: Help run Pinecreek Hills and New England’s Minuteman Valley Help the famous Park Rangers run Pinecreek Hills. Have fun organizing events on Bluewaters lake, Cherokee river and Apache trail. Learn about Wildlife. Camp & Picnic beside Rivers and Bayous. Explore atmospheric Waterfalls, Gorges, enchanted Caves and beautiful outdoor locations. Have fun on Hike & Bike Trails, go Paddleboarding, run a Pro Tour Fishing Tournament. Play great Hogs & Puzzles, Spot 100’s of Animals, Birds, Fish and Wildlife. Protect the environment, get Souvenirs and Awards along the way.
